profile:
Supreme Lock Solutions Ltd. is a locally owned company providing professional Locksmith/Safe/Security services to all of HRM and rural districts across Nova Scotia.

With over 30 years' experience in the security industry, Supreme Lock Solutions Ltd. specializes in the commercial end and offers a variety of locksmith, safe/vault, security products and services to meet your needs and budget.
